OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early low cloud in the east
OL,6,Fwill quickly clear. Otherwise, it will
OL,7,Fbe a dry day with plenty of sunshine
OL,8,Fand feeling very warm again.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA warm and sunny evening then
OL,11,Fremaining dry and clear overnight
OL,12,Facross all parts. The odd patchy of
OL,13,Fcloud will develop overnight.
OL,14,
OL,15,CTuesday:FAny early cloud will quickly
OL,16,Fclear, then another dry, sunny and
OL,17,Fvery warm day. Breezy along the County
OL,18,FDown coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
